{"tid":1178651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北俊:民陣反修例遊行人數重要","createTime":"2019-05-30T14:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:03:47.000Z","uid":137704,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e69231b4a8bf366cd2fdaabf4a8a02e308dd0db6","tid":1178651,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">田北俊:民陣反修例遊行人數重要</div><br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，不認為香港法庭在審理移交個案時有把關能力，<span style=\"color: red;\">個人意見認同要撤回修例</span>，但他認為中聯辦透過人大表明支持修例《逃犯條例》，立法會商界議員的投票意向已有結論。<span style=\"color: red;\">他又稱民陣6月9日反修例遊行人數重要，因為北京留意人數，判斷事件嚴重性。</span><br />\n<br />\n田北俊認為，修例由北京提出，所以中聯辦早前才會透過人大傳達中央意思，指有關做法即使當年《基本法》第23條立法時亦未曾有，所以相信商界議員投票取向已定。<br />\n<br />\n對於39名建制派立法會議員提出修訂，要求將移交門檻再提高至在港可判處7年刑期的罪名，及規定由當地最高司法機關提出的移交申請港府才受理。田北俊相信，有關建議乃中央已接納，所以建制派才會提出製造「成功爭取」的姿態。他又坦言，對未有提及追溯期感失望，但認為即使商界議員投票取向已決定，亦可以爭取更多，因為中央或會在商界支持修例下，接受多一兩項建議。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨葉劉淑儀指建制派建議過於偏袒商界，令不少嚴重罪行都豁免。田北俊認為，不少大眾都容易干犯的罪行，如重婚、毆打等，判刑都符合現有修訂的3年移交門檻，故他認為建制派建議門檻亦可消除大眾疑慮。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc0e31540b7a9aecf9eb0f7ab7998dbe7af2fa5","tid":1178651,"uid":137704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2150552/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A:%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81?fbclid=IwAR1ombKnRp2n6niFzy_-LDv9W91T6Yigvl-y7vnVq7tpfYhGam0UNh6smFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2150552%2F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BF%258A%3A%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ombKnRp2n6niFzy_-LDv9W91T6Yigvl-y7vnVq7tpfYhGam0UNh6smFE&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1cLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4f2ae300\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2150552/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A:%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81?fbclid=IwAR1ombKnRp2n6niFzy_-LDv9W91T6Yigvl-y7vnVq7tpfYhGam0UNh6smFE</a>"},{"pid":"3c8e69d175330b43bf29e327d5361d211b2c2175","tid":1178651,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"收皮喇 投票時最誠實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4113ad80bac82fcf6f1e047bc1951e38037d5f3b","tid":1178651,"uid":137704,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3c8e69d175330b43bf29e327d5361d211b2c2175","tid":1178651,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"收皮喇 投票時最誠實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"田北俊好誠實，當年廿三條言行一致投反對票"},{"pid":"bdeb945b61d2f09062aba3364f3825145268ccad","tid":1178651,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢先民主之父 23例都係靠佢</span>"},{"pid":"ee906d03c374deb4b9c046650ff7ea5e8592da3e","tid":1178651,"uid":251945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"自由黨又想反骨？"},{"pid":"7ac0c2cd3089f3a2960ce018604cc7a49344e5df","tid":1178651,"uid":191730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"田北俊認為，不少大眾都容易干犯的罪行，如<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重婚</strong></span>、毆打等，<br />\n<br />\n笑了，重婚抵拉啦<br />\n唔係大把人假結婚落黎香港"},{"pid":"de1cb5b4c7d5eab0ca642ab3b0a155ca193a8f84","tid":1178651,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命人數夠多啦"},{"pid":"410455b7d843069f66586ab899838d452e9a830e","tid":1178651,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"田少幾時出手呀"}]}